		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't care what license is attached, I will ignore it entirely if I decide to use any code from the wiki (seriously).  I predict most other people will as well. Knock yourself out, use whatever license gives you warm fuzzies.
<br />
<br />(edit)
<br />On second thought, I suggest using whatever license will encourage the most (or discourage the least) number of people to contribute.

		

