<br />fair enough, i just meant that a lot of the specifics could be ironed out while content is being added.  I often see good ideas for sites get bogged down in the details so I was just encouraging some forward movement.  but i'm new here so obviously i don't know all the reasons for why yall want things done certain ways <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

