<br />There's a word for this sort of discussion: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parkinson%27s_Law_of_Triviality" class="postlink">bike shed</a>. But copyright is one of the things that needs to be settled first because unlike pretty much everything else, it can't just be refactored out of the text of the wiki.

		

